What is Niuhuang Anxin Pills?
Niuhuang Anxin Pills are a time‑tested traditional Chinese medicine formulation based on realgar (Niuhuang) and other complementary herbs. The core pharmacological action is the clearing of internal heat and the detoxifying of harmful substances, with an ancillary calming effect on the nervous system. These pills are primarily prescribed for neurological conditions such as delirium, convulsions, palpitations, insomnia, and for patients experiencing acute stress responses. Their mode of action is believed to involve modulation of neurotransmitter pathways and stabilization of neuronal excitability, thereby providing immediate symptomatic relief and long‑term neuro‑protection.
